==English==
===Noun===
'''battle-cruiser'''

# A type of [[warship]] equal in size or larger than a contemporary [[battleship]], and of greater speed, but with less armour and fewer guns.  Introduced ca. 1908 and forming the leading squadrons of [[WWI]] battle fleets but [[obsolescent]] by WWII, having been replaced by the "fast battleship" type.

